# Google Places API — needed for auto-fetching reviews on the Reviews page
# 1. Go to https://console.cloud.google.com and create a project
# 2. Enable "Places API (New)"
# 3. Create an API key and restrict it to your domain
# 4. Find your Place ID at https://developers.google.com/maps/documentation/places/web-service/place-id
#    (search for "Kinza Hair & Beauty" or "Pinnacurl Illovo")

VITE_GOOGLE_PLACES_API_KEY=
VITE_GOOGLE_PLACE_ID=
